      ZWN_CechaOpis                   VARCHAR (   20)   CONSTRAINT DF_ZWN_CechaOpis DEFAULT('')         , --- CSTRING(21)
      CONSTRAINT ZWN_Primary PRIMARY KEY
        (
                          ZWN_Id                        
        )
  );
